node.text:
🔥FIRE UP THOSE ABS! Save & Try This Superset/Fat Burning Workout | Swipe➡️& Tag@ A Friend💪 @vqfit #motivation 
-
💥SUPERSETS: (A+B)
1A) Leg Over V-Sits - 3 x 8-10 Each Side
1B) Upper Crunch With Twist - 3 x 8-10 Each Side
2A) Lying Oblique Crunch - 3 x 10–12 Each Side
2B) Russian Twist + V-Sit - 3 x 8-10 Each Motion
3A) Alternate Leg V-Sits - 3 x 8-10 Each Leg
3B) Criss Cross/Bicycle - 3 x 10-12 Each Side
(90sec Rest Between Sets & 2min Between Exercises, DON’T BE A BITCH!)
-

💥Superset: (A+B)
1) Olympic Bar Upper Crunch - 4 x 10-12
2) Side To Side Leg Raises - 4 x  6-8 Each Side (AMRAP)
3A) Upper Crunch With Twist - 3 x 8-10 Each Side
3B) Kick Throughs - 3 x 25-30sec
4A) V-Sits - 3 x 12-15
4B) Squat Thrusts - 3 x 25-30sec
(90sec Rest Between Sets & 2min Between Exercises, DON’T BE A BITCH!)
